that asserted that sex crimes can be linked to hardcore 
pornography the panels stance represented an aboutface from the 
conclusion of another government commission in 1970 that there was 
no evidence of harm from pornography 
among other things hudsons panel recommended that congress 
force pornography traffickers to forfeit their profits and that 
